Plate Body: a flat, round or oval shape.
Parameters: body_radius=100, body_height=10
Orientation: body_origin=(0,0,0), body_normal=ZAxis

Plate Rim: a flat, round shape that is placed on the top edge of the plate body.
Parameters: rim_radius=body_radius, rim_height=2, rim_thickness=2
Orientation: rim_origin=body_origin, rim_normal=body_normal